features: COOLNESS THEY’LL LOVE: Give aspiring aviators something to smile about! Perfect for fun at the playground or indoors, these pullback aeroplane toys are a great way to keep the kiddies excitedly occupied. Every set comes with 2 toy planes for more fun.

FAST PULLBACK ACTION: No batteries needed to fuel the fun. Just pull back an airplane toy and watch it race across the floor. And these toy planes for kids aren’t just great for hours of imaginative play, they can also be used as super-cool aviation party decorations.

QUALITY YOU’LL LOVE: We’ve brought these die-cast airplanes to life using a mix of high-quality plastic and diecast metal. This means impressive durability to last through all that enthusiastic play indoors and outdoors.

MEMORIES THEY’LL CHERISH: Get on the floor, join in on the fun, and bond with your kiddo the extra-exciting way! Kids’ car toys are a great opportunity to spend quality time with little ones. They also foster independence during solo play and social skills during group play.

GREAT PARTY FAVORS: Looking for birthday party favors? A birthday or holiday gift any kiddo will cherish? These pull back airplanes make fine treats for kids. Also great as stocking stuffers, classroom prizes, and good behavior incentives. For ages 3+
